    21Ôćĺ
    22Ôćĺ    If the exception is intended, switch to :ref:`new-style hook wrappers
    23Ôćĺ    <hookwrappers>`, or use :func:`result.force_exception()
    24Ôćĺ    <pluggy.Result.force_exception>` to set the exception instead of raising.
    25Ôćĺ    """
    26Ôćĺ
    27Ôćĺ    __module__ = "pluggy"
